Effect of provincial spending on social services and health care on health 
outcomes in Canada: an observational longitudinal study.

Dutton DJ(1), Forest PG(2), Kneebone RD(2), Zwicker JD(2).

Author information:
(1)School of Public Policy, University of Calgary, Calgary, Alta. 
djdutton@ucalgary.ca.
